{"tid":661710,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"(有圖)賣病貓及冒充他人身份","createTime":"2018-05-11T20:31:43.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-12T11:28:15.000Z","uid":186416,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"384851f567b0df1d2cbb01f93685a8de67419ff0","tid":661710,"uid":186416,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-11T20:31:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/12/034703_34e3f57e4748376fb965bf5eac5503bd.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F12%2F034703_34e3f57e4748376fb965bf5eac5503bd.png&h=6c5921b7&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/12/034704_a0169e7c7a9af67d906f9bb3d804f0d3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F12%2F034704_a0169e7c7a9af67d906f9bb3d804f0d3.png&h=90262f33&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n這名人士程光頭王，David Wong<br />\n此人在Facebook以自家繁殖為名到處賣病貓，大部份貓隻岀售後均死去<br />\n<br />\n事源本人係一個以貓作交流既聊天群裡面，這面叫光頭王既男子，報程自己做繁殖生意2,30年，平日係群入面都會講一d關於繁殖上既野，但係內容裡面已經感覺倒毫無根據，缺乏常理，例如貓互相可以亂倫，近親繁殖之類...<br />\n後尾有一個新群組成員加入，呢個光頭王突然叫Admin踢除新成員，我地先係新成員口中得知賣病貓事兒，當事件曝光後，王生自行離去，但原來分身仲係群入面，並將群組裡面既成員電話及頭像偷取，係Facebook 上面開設假post，並引誘他人致電造成騷擾，圖片如下<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/12/042141_81430b1833225b98b104f9020d9df41e.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F12%2F042141_81430b1833225b98b104f9020d9df41e.png&h=a6fe6995&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/12/042144_67056bfcb1ef8e947827db946144383d.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F12%2F042144_67056bfcb1ef8e947827db946144383d.png&h=12eabeb4&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/12/042146_a0136f446dfb12651e46fe9046bd4e67.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F12%2F042146_a0136f446dfb12651e46fe9046bd4e67.png&h=0915181b&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/12/042150_d2ddb44178ba99c849c79108456868c8.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F12%2F042150_d2ddb44178ba99c849c79108456868c8.png&h=8daf3fe9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n對他人做成極大困擾！以上事件已經唔係發生過一次，呢件事係昨日發生，現提供有限度資料如下<br />\n<br />\n此人士特徵：通常會用 王,Wong,文,Man等字眼改名<br />\n頭像會用女人，超人等圖片，大部分Account 都係新開<br />\n電話:59384885,53657633<br />\n<br />\n現在希望各位如發現此人行蹤，可以留言提供線索或分享岀去，如有地址也歡迎提供。"},{"pid":"9fbd05ffb97a8ac1710ae9e6a82a0765f079783e","tid":661710,"uid":186416,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-11T20:43:37.000Z","msg":"本人少開Post,如有錯字及1999,多多包涵"},{"pid":"eacc1e21647dbd6f10cd004d953b19ef05f46811","tid":661710,"uid":185092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-11T20:53:52.000Z","msg":"貓可以亂倫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> WTF"},{"pid":"39173c4ca9abe27194c280dbc85eb0c58bd9319f","tid":661710,"uid":136039,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-11T21:27:39.000Z","msg":"fb好多貓貓交易group都成日有人話呢條友賣病貓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n出曬名"},{"pid":"fbffe7cd200c659fef0cf1fcd3d4e4524a321650","tid":661710,"uid":186416,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"eacc1e21647dbd6f10cd004d953b19ef05f46811","tid":661710,"uid":185092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-11T20:53:52.000Z","msg":"貓可以亂倫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> WTF"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-11T21:34:47.000Z","msg":"喪失病狂啊，話咩貓無亂倫，係佢地天性，好撚痴線"},{"pid":"1c79a72d8d2c90d686e2b53088c70379723b3e82","tid":661710,"uid":186416,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"39173c4ca9abe27194c280dbc85eb0c58bd9319f","tid":661710,"uid":136039,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime"